HEADWORD: Vecture
<hw>Vec"ture</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>vectura</ets>, from <ets>vehere</ets>, <ets>vectum</ets>, to carry.
Cf. <er>Vettura</er>, <er>Voiture</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of carrying;
conveyance; carriage.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
